graph LR
    MRO[Model Registry Operator]

    %% External Platform Dependencies (Required)
    MRO -->|reconciliation| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>Required]
    MRO -->|certificate mgmt| OpenShiftCA[OpenShift Service CA<br/>Required]

    %% External Database Dependencies (Required - one of)
    MRO -.->|auto-provision| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL 16+<br/>Required or MySQL]
    MRO -.->|manual provision| MySQL[MySQL 8.0+<br/>Required or PostgreSQL]

    %% External Optional Dependencies
    MRO -.->|optional cert mgmt| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>Optional]
    MRO -.->|optional service mesh| Istio[Istio Service Mesh 1.20+<br/>Optional]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    MRO -->|catalog data| ODHMetadata[odh-model-metadata-collection<br/>Internal ODH]
    MRO -.->|optional service mesh auth| Authorino[Authorino<br/>Internal ODH Optional]

    %% Platform Services
    MRO -->|external exposure| OpenShiftRouter[OpenShift Router<br/>Platform]
    MRO -->|authentication| OpenShiftOAuth[OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>Platform]
    MRO -->|monitoring| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Platform]

    %% Model Registry Instance Components (Created by Operator)
    MRO -->|creates/manages| RestAPI[Model Registry REST API]
    MRO -->|creates/manages| OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy<br/>Optional]
    MRO -->|creates/manages| RBACProxy[kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Optional]
    MRO -->|creates/manages| gRPCAPI[gRPC API<br/>Deprecated]

    %% Model Registry Dependencies
    RestAPI -->|metadata storage| PostgreSQL
    RestAPI -->|metadata storage| MySQL
    OAuthProxy -->|token validation| OpenShiftOAuth
    RBACProxy -->|authz checks| K8sAPI

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Optional Integration] -.->|UI management| RestAPI
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Optional Integration] -.->|model registration| RestAPI

    %% Styling
    style MRO fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff
    style K8sAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OpenShiftCA fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OpenShiftRouter fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OpenShiftOAuth fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Prometheus fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    style PostgreSQL fill:#9b59b6,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style MySQL fill:#9b59b6,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Istio fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    style ODHMetadata fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Authorino fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    style RestAPI fill:#3498db,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style OAuthProxy fill:#3498db,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5,color:#fff
    style RBACProxy fill:#3498db,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5,color:#fff
